headline: Up Nearly 40% Since August, This Hot Technology Stock's Growth Is Just Getting Started
summary: Positioning and workflow technology company Trimble (NASDAQ: TRMB) isn't the easiest company to understand.  Here's why Trimble is an outstanding stock to buy now.  Despite trading in negative territory when compared to January 2022, Trimble's stock is up 34% in 2024 and a whopping 75% over the last year.
